                    "`t`t`t`tOpen archive",
                    "`t`t`t`tExtract Here",
                    "`t`t`t`tExtract to <Folder>",
                    "`t`t`t`tAdd to <Archive>.zip",
                    "`t`t`t`tCRC SHA >",
                    "Wait for the process to close (custom script): WaitWhileProcess 7zFM"
                ]
            }
